{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "paymob-flow-1234-5678-90ab-cdef12345678",
    "name": "Paymob Payment Flow - Subscription Upgrade",
    "description": "Complete payment flow documentation for Paymob integration. This collection demonstrates the entire flow from initiating a subscription upgrade to verifying payment status and upgrading user to premium.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1. Initiate Subscription Upgrade",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Upgrade to Premium (EGP)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status code is 200', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Response has success status', function () {",
                  "    const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.status).to.eql('success');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Payment URL is returned', function () {",
                  "    const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.data).to.have.property('paymentUrl');",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.data.paymentUrl).to.be.a('string');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Intention ID is returned', function () {",
                  "    const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.data).to.have.property('intentionId');",
                  "    ",
                  "    // Save intention ID for next requests",
                  "    pm.environment.set('intention_id', jsonData.data.intentionId);",
                  "    pm.environment.set('transaction_id', jsonData.data.transaction._id || jsonData.data.transaction);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Transaction is created', function () {",
                  "    const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.data).to.have.property('transaction');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            },
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "// Ensure you have a valid auth token",
                  "// This endpoint requires authentication"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{auth_token}}",
                "description": "JWT token from login"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"currency\": \"EGP\",\n  \"billingCycle\": \"monthly\",\n  \"autoRenew\": true,\n  \"paymentMethod\": \"credit_card\",\n  \"billingData\": {\n    \"firstName\": \"Ahmed\",\n    \"lastName\": \"Mohamed\",\n    \"email\": \"ahmed@example.com\",\n    \"phoneNumber\": \"+201234567890\",\n    \"apartment\": \"Apt 5B\",\n    \"floor\": \"3rd Floor\",\n    \"street\": \"123 Main Street\",\n    \"building\": \"Building A\",\n    \"country\": \"EGY\",\n    \"state\": \"Cairo\"\n  }\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/subscriptions/upgrade",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "subscriptions", "upgrade"]
            },
            "description": "**Step 1: Initiate Subscription Upgrade**\n\nThis endpoint:\n1. Creates/updates subscription with `status: 'pending'` and `plan: 'premium'`\n2. Creates transaction with `status: 'pending'` and `type: 'subscription_payment'`\n3. Creates Paymob payment intention\n4. Saves `intentionId` in transaction metadata\n5. Returns `paymentUrl` to redirect user to Paymob\n\n**Required:**\n- Authentication token (Student role)\n- Currency: EGP (for Paymob integration)\n\n**Response includes:**\n- `paymentUrl`: URL to redirect user to Paymob payment page\n- `intentionId`: Paymob payment intention ID (save this!)\n- `transaction`: Transaction ID\n- `clientSecret`: Paymob client secret"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Success Response",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Content-Type",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  },
                  {
                    "key": "Authorization",
                    "value": "Bearer {{auth_token}}"
                  }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"currency\": \"EGP\",\n  \"billingCycle\": \"monthly\"\n}"
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/subscriptions/upgrade",
                  "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
                  "path": ["api", "v1", "subscriptions", "upgrade"]
                }
              },
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [
                {
                  "key": "Content-Type",
                  "value": "application/json"
                }
              ],
              "cookie": [],
              "body": "{\n  \"status\": \"success\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"subscription\": {\n      \"_id\": \"...\",\n      \"plan\": \"premium\",\n      \"status\": \"pending\"\n    },\n    \"transaction\": \"...\",\n    \"paymentUrl\": \"https://accept.paymob.com/payment/...\",\n    \"clientSecret\": \"...\",\n    \"intentionId\": \"pi_test_9399040f087b41d0b8c7ac37a2d56c5a\",\n    \"message\": \"Please complete payment with Paymob\"\n  }\n}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "description": "**Step 1: User initiates subscription upgrade**\n\nAfter this step:\n- User should be redirected to `paymentUrl`\n- User completes payment on Paymob\n- Paymob will call webhook and redirect user back"
    },
    {
      "name": "2. Paymob Webhook (Payment Status Update)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Simulate Paymob Webhook - Success",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status code is 200', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Webhook processed successfully', function () {",
                  "    const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.status).to.eql('success');",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.message).to.include('processed successfully');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "console.log('Webhook processed - Transaction status updated to completed');",
                  "console.log('Subscription upgraded to premium');",
                  "console.log('User profile updated to premium tier');"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"type\": \"TRANSACTION\",\n  \"obj\": {\n    \"id\": 192036465,\n    \"pending\": false,\n    \"amount_cents\": 100000,\n    \"success\": true,\n    \"is_auth\": false,\n    \"is_capture\": false,\n    \"is_standalone_payment\": true,\n    \"is_voided\": false,\n    \"is_refunded\": false,\n    \"is_3d_secure\": true,\n    \"integration_id\": 4097558,\n    \"order\": {\n      \"id\": \"{{intention_id}}\",\n      \"amount_cents\": 100000,\n      \"currency\": \"EGP\"\n    },\n    \"created_at\": \"2024-01-15T10:30:00Z\",\n    \"currency\": \"EGP\",\n    \"source_data\": {\n      \"type\": \"card\",\n      \"sub_type\": \"visa\",\n      \"pan\": \"1234\"\n    }\n  }\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/paymob/webhook",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "paymob", "webhook"]
            },
            "description": "**Step 2A: Paymob Webhook Callback (PRIMARY)**\n\n**Called by:** Paymob server automatically when payment is processed\n\n**What happens:**\n1. Receives webhook data from Paymob\n2. Processes webhook and extracts `isPaid: true` if payment successful\n3. Finds transaction by `intentionId`\n4. Updates `transaction.status = 'completed'` ✅\n5. If payment successful:\n   - Updates subscription: `status: 'active'`, `plan: 'premium'` ✅\n   - Updates user: `studentProfile.subscriptionTier = 'premium'` ✅\n   - Creates notification ✅\n\n**Note:** This is the PRIMARY source of truth. Paymob calls this automatically.\n\n**To test:** Replace `{{intention_id}}` with actual intention ID from Step 1"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Success Response",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Content-Type",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"type\": \"TRANSACTION\",\n  \"obj\": {\n    \"id\": 192036465,\n    \"success\": true,\n    \"pending\": false,\n    \"amount_cents\": 100000,\n    \"order\": {\n      \"id\": \"pi_test_9399040f087b41d0b8c7ac37a2d56c5a\"\n    },\n    \"currency\": \"EGP\"\n  }\n}"
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/paymob/webhook",
                  "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
                  "path": ["api", "v1", "paymob", "webhook"]
                }
              },
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
