      "description": "**Step 2A: Paymob Webhook (PRIMARY)**\n\nThis is called automatically by Paymob when payment status changes.\n\n**What it does:**\n- Updates transaction status to 'completed' if payment successful\n- Upgrades subscription to premium\n- Updates user profile to premium tier\n- Creates notification"
    },
    {
      "name": "3. Success Redirect Callback",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Payment Success Redirect",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status code is 302 (Redirect)', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(302);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Redirects to frontend', function () {",
                  "    const location = pm.response.headers.get('Location');",
                  "    pm.expect(location).to.include('/payment/processing');",
                  "    pm.expect(location).to.include('id=');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "console.log('Success callback processed');",
                  "console.log('Transaction status updated to completed');",
                  "console.log('Subscription upgraded to premium');",
                  "console.log('User redirected to frontend');"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/paymob/success?id={{intention_id}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "paymob", "success"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "id",
                  "value": "{{intention_id}}",
                  "description": "Payment intention ID from Step 1"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "**Step 2B: Success Redirect Callback (FALLBACK)**\n\n**Called by:** Paymob redirects user here after successful payment\n\n**What happens:**\n1. Receives `id` (intentionId) from query parameter\n2. Finds transaction by `intentionId`\n3. Updates `transaction.status = 'completed'` ✅\n4. If transaction type is `'subscription_payment'`:\n   - Updates subscription: `plan: 'premium'`, `status: 'active'` ✅\n   - Updates user: `studentProfile.subscriptionTier = 'premium'` ✅\n   - Creates notification ✅\n5. Redirects to: `${FRONTEND_URL}/payment/processing?id=${id}`\n\n**Note:** This is a FALLBACK. The webhook (Step 2A) is the primary source of truth.\n\n**To test:** Replace `{{intention_id}}` with actual intention ID from Step 1"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Redirect Response",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [],
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/paymob/success?id=pi_test_9399040f087b41d0b8c7ac37a2d56c5a",
                  "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
                  "path": ["api", "v1", "paymob", "success"],
                  "query": [
                    {
                      "key": "id",
                      "value": "pi_test_9399040f087b41d0b8c7ac37a2d56c5a"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              },
              "status": "Found",
              "code": 302,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "html",
              "header": [
                {
                  "key": "Location",
                  "value": "http://localhost:3000/payment/processing?id=pi_test_9399040f087b41d0b8c7ac37a2d56c5a"
                }
              ],
              "cookie": [],
              "body": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "description": "**Step 2B: Success Redirect (FALLBACK)**\n\nThis is called when Paymob redirects the user back after payment.\n\n**What it does:**\n- Updates transaction status to 'completed'\n- Upgrades subscription to premium\n- Updates user profile to premium tier\n- Redirects user to frontend"
    },
    {
      "name": "4. Check Payment Status",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Payment Status",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status code is 200', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Response has success status', function () {",
                  "    const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.status).to.eql('success');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Payment status is returned', function () {",
                  "    const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.data).to.have.property('paymentStatus');",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.data).to.have.property('isPaid');",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.data.isPaid).to.be.a('boolean');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Intention ID matches', function () {",
                  "    const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.data.intentionId).to.eql(pm.environment.get('intention_id'));",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "// Log payment status",
                  "const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "console.log('Payment Status:', jsonData.data.paymentStatus);",
                  "console.log('Is Paid:', jsonData.data.isPaid);",
                  "console.log('Transaction Status:', jsonData.data.paymentStatus === 'PROCESSED' ? 'Completed' : 'Pending/Failed');",
                  "",
                  "if (jsonData.data.isPaid) {",
                  "    console.log('✅ Payment successful! User upgraded to premium.');",
                  "} else {",
                  "    console.log('⏳ Payment still pending or failed.');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/paymob/payment-status?id={{intention_id}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "paymob", "payment-status"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "id",
                  "value": "{{intention_id}}",
                  "description": "Payment intention ID from Step 1"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "**Step 3: Check Payment Status**\n\n**Called by:** Frontend polling after redirect from Paymob\n\n**What happens:**\n1. Receives `id` (intentionId) from query parameter\n2. Finds transaction by `intentionId`\n3. Returns payment status from database\n4. Returns `isPaid: true` if `transaction.status === 'completed'`\n\n**Response when payment is successful:**\n```json\n{\n  \"status\": \"success\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"intentionId\": \"pi_test_...\",\n    \"paymentStatus\": \"PROCESSED\",\n    \"isPaid\": true,\n    \"transactionId\": \"...\",\n    \"amount\": 100,\n    \"currency\": \"EGP\",\n    \"type\": \"subscription_payment\",\n    \"completedAt\": 1234567890\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**Response when payment is pending:**\n```json\n{\n  \"status\": \"success\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"paymentStatus\": \"PENDING\",\n    \"isPaid\": false\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**To test:** Replace `{{intention_id}}` with actual intention ID from Step 1"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Payment Successful",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [],
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/paymob/payment-status?id=pi_test_9399040f087b41d0b8c7ac37a2d56c5a",
                  "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
                  "path": ["api", "v1", "paymob", "payment-status"],
                  "query": [
                    {
                      "key": "id",
                      "value": "pi_test_9399040f087b41d0b8c7ac37a2d56c5a"
                    }
